name: Somnolence
description:
This large 16 x 20 animal portrait of an elephant was done completely in pencil on high quality drawing paper(its really thick). A portrait of this size is normally $150.00, but right now this beautiful portrait is marked  all the way down to $100.00 a savings of $50.00.
   Since this is done on high quality paper in pencil, there is no clear coat.

name: Custom Artwork
description:
Send us a message before you make the purchase....The price of custom artwork is a 30 dollar minimum! 
An 8 x 10 portrait done in pencil is normally $75.00,right now during Sale, 8 x 10 portraits are only $50.00. Tell us in detail what art you would like or send us a picture of what you want. Also what size you would want:

Small Rectangle Wood plaque is 5 x 7 in
Large Rectangle Wood plaque is 8 x 11 in (about the size of a piece of computer paper)
     We will also do custom drawings on paper sold in a frame, this includes portraits of people and animals. Just send us a message on what you want , and what your budget is for the custom artwork. We look forward to hearing from you. Wood-burning's and drawings always have at least a small amount of clear coat sprayed on them for preservation purposes.

name: Fairy Garden 8"in x 11"in
description: This is a larger piece at 8"in x 11"in. .A beautiful piece of morning glories and fairies with vibrant colors to catch the eye. Belief in fairies has existed from earliest times, and literature's all over the world have tales of fairies and their relations with humans.
